  - Hierarchy: Bold for headings and CTAs; regular/light for body
- Components
  - Cards: 8–12px radius; subtle shadows; hover scale with bronze accent
  - Buttons: Bronze-gold fill (#A97C50), white or navy text; secondary beige with bronze outline
  - Forms: Subtle inputs with sand backgrounds; clear focus ring in accent
