  - CloudinaryUploader: handles file selection, client-side validation, and direct upload to Cloudinary (or via API if signed uploads).
  - ImageCropper: client-side cropping UI with aspect ratios per use-case; outputs crop data and image blob for upload.
  - MediaGalleryEditor: listing/profile/editorial gallery with add/remove/reorder, thumbnails, and alt/caption editing.
