  - Use useState with arrays initialized to []: const [assets, setAssets] = useState<MediaAsset[]>([]);
  - Guard all array operations: (assets ?? []).map(...), Array.isArray(assets) ? assets.map(...) : [].
  - When receiving API data (e.g., response.data), validate: const list = Array.isArray(response?.data) ? response.data : [].
